HEADWORD: Yelp
<hw>Yelp</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A sharp, quick cry; a bark.</def>
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

